text: Command Performance is a 2009 American action movie directed by Dolph Lundgren (who also stars). It also starring Melissa Smith, Hristo Shopov, Zahary Baharov, Dave Legeno, Yulian Vergov, Raicho Vasilev and Clement von Franckenstein. ==Other websites== * * * Category:2009 action movies Category:American action movies Category:Movies set in Moscow Category:Movies set in the 1990s Category:Movies directed by Dolph Lundgren Category:Movies about terrorism
